com.rohitkalhans.sedna.io

Class SedaQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rohitkalhans.sedna.io.SedaQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Lifecycle

    public class SedaQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements Lifecycle
    Abstraction of ActiveMQ which will be used as input and output queues. The inbound and the outbound queues will be used by default unless the output is directed to a different queues as specified in the OutputCollector.write().
